            "The article assesses the&nbsp;quality of automated information systems for managing the&nbsp;educational process and selects an approach for designing web- and mobile applications.<br><br>The architecture of the&nbsp;software complex is presented: <br>1. The&nbsp;&laquo;1C: College PROF&raquo; information system, which implements modules for initial data, competency calculation, and reporting. <br>2. The&nbsp;student's personal account website, which serves as a&nbsp;module for presenting student results. <br>3. The&nbsp;mobile application for the&nbsp;employment manager, which facilitates interaction with employers. <br>4. The&nbsp;client-server architecture of the&nbsp;software complex, which has a&nbsp;three-tier architecture and implements an integration module.<br><br>",
